title: Meet Travel Insurance Center at the Agent@Home Travel Summit in Long Beach
text:
Last updated: 04:54 PM ET, Tue August 25 2015 Meet Travel Insurance Center at the Agent@Home Travel Summit in Long Beach Travel Agent | Claudette Covey | August 25, 2015 
In today’s uncertain world, it has never been more important for agents to ensure that their clients are armed with the proper travel insurance. 
Travel Insurance Center, a travel aggregator, helps agents determine just that. Agents and their clients are able to compare, shop for and buy travel insurance through the company’s online Policy Picker tool or with the help of licensed travel insurance agents over the phone. < Do you want to read the full story? You must be a registered travel professional with an active account to view the full story. Are you a Travel Agent? Log in to your account now, or register for free!
